---
title: Sizzling Garlic Herb Butter Steak with Roasted Broccoli plus Honey-Glazed Peas & Carrots
description: Steak is never more satisfying than when it’s sizzled just the way you like it. When you hear the hiss and pop of hot oil on a pan and hit it with a tender piece of beef, you know it’s going to be a great night. Elevated by a dollop of butter speckled with herbaceous thyme and infused with savory garlic, Worcestershire sauce, and pepper, you couldn’t ask for a more sumptuous centerpiece to your plate than this juicy steak. On the side are crisp, golden potato wedges and honey-kissed carrots and peas.
